useAuthorizationHeader - Variable in class org.gerstner.oauth2android.Server
Flag to indicate if the server preferres the use of the "Authorization" Http-Header.
useAuthorizationHeader(boolean) - Method in class org.gerstner.oauth2android.Server
May be set to false to force the client to include the access token in the requests url or request body instead of using the http "Authorization" request header.
useAuthorizationHeader() - Method in class org.gerstner.oauth2android.Server
Returns the state of the authorization header flag Server.useAuthorizationHeader.
